# CI-generated. The release workflow's `stage bundled scoutsuite` step
# downloads/freezes the per-platform binaries into these directories and
# writes pinned.json with the SHA-256 build.rs reads. Local development
# can populate these too (see `vendor/scoutsuite/docker/iterate.sh` for
# the local-iteration path), but the artifacts are never tracked —
# release.yml is the single source of truth.

# ScoutSuite per-platform PyInstaller-frozen binaries + the SHA pin.
scoutsuite/*/
scoutsuite/pinned.json

# Reserved for a future Terraform binary bundling pipeline (Phase 2 of
# the plan drops Terraform entirely, so this entry is defensive). If
# Phase 2 lands first the second block can be removed.
terraform/*/
terraform/pinned.json
